        "TileImage": "$($repository 9b0d0651-4f81-40e5-bf2a-5aec6fd763a5).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\r\rYou have been tasked with intereupting a munitions deal between Kronstadt Industries and the United States military. Once the chief researcher on the matter and the middle man/lobbyist have been taken care of, the agreement should fall apart.\r\rThough, while you&apos;re on the ground, they would like you to take care of a few rebelious employees. A double-crossing corporate spy undercover as a guard, and a mechanic who stole trade secrets.\r\rGood luck, and be careful.",
